https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Horigome_S.description: Horigome Station (堀米駅, Horigome-eki) is a railway station on the Tobu Sano Line in Sano, Tochigi, Japan, operated by the private railway operator Tobu Railway. The station is numbered "TI-35".
